  The plaintext reveals the setup for Stage 9:
    * Stage 9 message is DES-encrypted.
    * Leftmost byte of the DES key is binary 110100111 (stated in the text).
    * Schlussel 0716150413020110 is the full DES key.
    * DEBUGGER.BIN (346780fe5d4dfcf1) = DES("DEBUGGER") with that key.
      This is a verification value / known-plaintext hint for Stage 9.


